# =============================================================================
# CONTRACT ADDRESSES
# =============================================================================
# Contract addresses are loaded from: frontend/addresses.json
#
# This file is auto-generated from contract deployments and contains:
# - Swag1155 Designs (each Design is a separate contract instance)
# - FaucetManager (ETH faucet)
# - ZKPassportNFT (sybil resistance)
#
# IMPORTANT: Swag1155 Design Architecture
# - Each Design is deployed as a separate contract
# - Multiple Design addresses can exist per network
# - Design addresses are stored in frontend/addresses.json or can be
#   configured via environment variables if needed
#
# Example Design address configuration (if needed):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DESIGN_1_ADDRESS_BASE=0x...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DESIGN_1_ADDRESS_ETHEREUM=0x...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DESIGN_1_ADDRESS_UNICHAIN=0x...
#
# To update addresses:
# 1. Deploy contracts using your deployment scripts
# 2. The frontend/ folder is updated automatically
# 3. Commit the changes to version control
#
# DO NOT hardcode contract addresses in .env - use frontend/addresses.json
# =============================================================================
